name: Yowamushi Pedal - Ashita e no High Cadence [3DS]
description:
Yowamushi Pedal: Ashita e no High Cadence is an arcade game developed by Bandai Namco Entertainment. It was originally released in 2015. It was published by Bandai Namco Entertainment.
Yowamushi Pedal: Ashita e no High Cadence is available on Nintendo 3DS.
